data.description: Excellent value on this 4BR pool home in the desirable Lake Kehoe Preserve neighborhood. Room for everyone and everything! Layout boasts common living space, master suite, laundry & half bath on the ground floor with remaining bedrooms/bath and bonus loft space upstairs. Step inside to space formally designed as formal living and dining space – versatile to arrange to suit your needs. Walk back to the heart of the home – open, spacious kitchen and family room. Kitchen boasts granite counters, attractive tile backsplash, stainless appliances, recessed lighting, large closet pantry, and plenty of room to arrange casual dining space. The family room makes for a great gathering space and provides direct access to the pool deck. Split bedroom plan with master suite downstairs. You will be impressed with the size of the bedroom, as it includes a nine foot alcove which would be ideal as a sitting area or private office. The contemporary bath includes a dual sink vanity, soaker tub and separate shower. And you will love the 16x11 master closet – perfect for all your personal storage needs. Remaining bedrooms/bath are tucked off the home’s upstairs hallway – each generous in size. You’ll also be wow’d by the size of the loft. This flex space would be ideal as a secondary entertainment spot, or a place for hobbies, fitness gear, or a home office. Another plus: the home has extra storage space in both the loft and under the main staircase. One big reason to want to own this home is all that you have out back – pristine pool under screen enclosure with a treed conservation area behind. Having no rear neighbors gives you privacy to enjoy fun in the sun. Great location, too - Lake Kehoe Preserve is a secure, gated community of well- maintained homes. It features a boardwalk and observation deck on Lake Kehoe which is only a minute’s walk from your house – here you can enjoy some quiet time while taking in nature’s glory. You’re only a 5-minute drive to SR 408 and 10 minutes to Waterford Lakes shopping center, so easy access to shopping and dining. You’ll love living here. Come see all that this special home has to offer!
